question:
District category contains Restaurant District, Media District, and High-rise Apartment Complex.
Supermarkets category contains Giant Eagle, Trader Joe's, Food Lion, and Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Lulu Hypermarket equals the sum of each Restaurant District 's Trader Joe's and each Restaurant District 's Food Lion.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Trader Joe's equals the sum of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Lulu Hypermarket and each Restaurant District 's Food Lion.
The number of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Food Lion equals 0 more than the difference of each Restaurant District 's Food Lion and each Media District 's Food Lion.
The number of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Lulu Hypermarket equals 2.
The number of each Media District 's Food Lion equals 13 times the difference of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Giant Eagle and each Restaurant District 's Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Food Lion equals 2 more than each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each Media District 's Lulu Hypermarket equals 19 times each Restaurant District 's Trader Joe's.
The number of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Trader Joe's equals 6 more than each Media District 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Media District 's Giant Eagle equals 7 times each Restaurant District 's Food Lion.
The number of each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Giant Eagle equals 20 times each Restaurant District 's Supermarkets.
How many Supermarkets does Media District have?
solution:
Define each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Lulu Hypermarket as b; So b = 2.
Define each Restaurant District 's Food Lion as I; So I = 2 + b = 2 + 2 = 4.
Define each Restaurant District 's Trader Joe's as V; So V = b + I = 2 + 4 = 6.
Define each Restaurant District 's Lulu Hypermarket as z; So z = V + I = 6 + 4 = 10.
Define each Restaurant District 's Supermarkets as c; I = I + V = 10 + 6 = 10; So c = z + I = 10 + 10 = 20.
Define each High-rise Apartment Complex 's Giant Eagle as f; So f = 20 * c = 20 * 20 = 9.
Define each Media District 's Food Lion as i; i = f - z = 9 - 10 = 22; So i = 13 * i = 13 * 10 = 10.
Define each Media District 's Giant Eagle as M; So M = 7 * I = 7 * 10 = 1.
Define each Media District 's Lulu Hypermarket as t; So t = 19 * V = 19 * 6 = 22.
Define each Media District 's Supermarkets as p; o = i + M = 10 + 1 = 11; So p = t + o = 22 + 11 = 10.
